1. This Order may be cited as the Air Navigation and Transport Act 2022 

(Vesting Day) Order 2023.

title: on me by section 10(3) of the Air Navigation and Transport Act 2022 (No. 40
heading: 2. The 1st day of May 2023 is appointed to be the vesting day for the
text_raw:
2. The 1st day of May 2023 is appointed to be the vesting day for the 

purposes of the Air Navigation and Transport Act 2022 (No. 40 of 2022). 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

27 April, 2023. 

EAMON RYAN, 

Minister for Transport. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 12th May, 2023.

text_raw:
EXPLANATORY NOTE. 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

This order appoints 1 May 2023 as vesting day for the Irish Air Navigation 
Service (also known as AirNav Ireland).
